Terrain - Class in edu.cnm.deepdive.ca.rps.models
This class models cyclic dominance in a simplified ecosystem as a form of the game Rock-Paper-Scissors, played on a toroidal terrain.

Terrain.Neighborhood - Enum in edu.cnm.deepdive.ca.rps.models
This class enumerates 2 commonly used neighborhoods for determining adjacency in a number of 2-dimensional cellular automata (CA) and similar models.
